# MCP territory-ia — default retrieval

When **territory-ia** tools are available (Cursor Agent + MCP enabled), use them first: **`backlog_issue`** for a known issue id, then specs, glossary, router table, invariants, and rule bodies. See `AGENTS.md` step 3 and `docs/mcp-ia-server.md`. Avoid loading full `.cursor/specs/*.md` files when `spec_section` or `spec_outline` suffices.
